35TTC Issuance Schedule

TTC
Protocol

The value of TTC tokens depends on advertising costs, inde-
pendent of the influence of exchange. TTC tokens will expe-
rience fluctuations in value similar to what’ s seen on other 
advertising platforms, such as toutiao.com. A user could 
contribute $0.15 USD per month when the number of users 
is relatively small, but this figure could be around $1.5 USD 
when the number of users in the platform reaches a certain 
threshold. The ActiveRate begins at 100, dropping to around 
42% and going up to 50% as the number of users increase. 
This value is based on industry standards and the perfor-
mance of tataUFO.

MAU = TotalUser*ActiveRate
USDValueperTTC(withoutExchage) =   AdsRevenueEachMonth 
                                                                                                TTCEachMonth

=  MAUEachMonth*AdsWeight
