TTC Pre-Initial Token Sale
and Initial Token Sale plan

TTC tokens will be issued on ERC-20 with a total amount of 
1,000,000,000 (1 billion), in which 25% of the total number 
of TTC tokens will be set aside for sale. Participants in the 
pre-initial token sale ( “Pre-Initial Token Sale” ) and initial 
token sale (“Initial Token Sale”) can purchase TTC with ETH. 

